<plot>In this European semi-version of "Take Care of My Little Girl, Lorna (Susan Stephen), the daughter of an American playboy, enters a girls' school,in the Alps, for the international smart-set,where the main course of study appears to be the study of how to trap a rich man. At first, she is dominated and looked down on by the school ring-leaders and forced into rooming with ---horrors---a scholarship student. But when a rich young American shows interest in her she is elevated to the international clique of the upper-termers. She then---horrors again---falls in love with a poor local mountaineer.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?189071</url></doc>
